              <h4>StudentEB5</h4>
              <p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 0 0 15px;">Your Path to Permanent Residency</p>
              <p style="color: #888; font-size: 0.85rem; margin: 0;">Free educational resources for international students and H-1B professionals exploring EB-5 investment immigration.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>Quick Links</h4>
              <nav aria-label="Footer quick links">
                <a href="/">Home</a>
                <a href="/about">About Us</a>
